      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "Truly appreciate the warm hearted team in Woon Ho for their kind care to my uncle whom is suffering from physically weakness  n also dementia and then passed away peacefully in the home. The team in the process send videos and updates to my cousin ( his daughter whom reside in spore). They also help seek medical assistance n help to monitor his condition thoroughly. During the ending of his journey , they also helped to let him feel comfortable by monitoring his food n breathing. They also helped contact caretaker n help arrange everything for the funeral before my cousin rushed in fr spore. We sincerely appreciate their help. Thank you. We need more kind people like you all 🙏🏻",
      "textTranslated": null,
      "publishAt": "10 months ago",
