      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 3,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "As a physiotherapist currently working with some of the elderly at this center, I can attest that they are well taken care of. Despite some of my patients are still being bedridden, none of them suffer from bed sores. Additionally, the center has nurses and caretakers who monitor the elderly's vital signs and overall health.",
