      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 2,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "很有愛心和责任感的疗养院，价格很合理，Ms Ho和他的先生都很有责任感，护士团队很棒，环境好，很有家的感觉，谢谢何小姐和他的先生还有那里的护士团队，也曾经很细心的照顾我的母亲，让她有个happy ending 🙏🙏🙏👍👍👍👍👍👍",
      "textTranslated": "A very loving and responsible nursing home. The prices are very reasonable. Ms. Ho and her husband are very responsible, the nursing team is excellent, and the environment is pleasant and feels very homey. Thank you Ms. Ho and her husband, as well as the nursing team, for taking such good care of my mother and helping her have a happy ending. 🙏🙏🙏👍👍👍👍👍👍",
